cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely sub-category because the paper deals with iterative expansion of a set of initial seed instances, which is a common technique in machine learning. 

cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible sub-category because the paper deals with extracting relationships from text, which is a common task in information retrieval.
